casebody.data:
Gerald WARD, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
BAYONNE INDUSTRIES, INC., East Jersey Railroad & Terminal Co., and Bayonne Terminal Warehouse Corp., Defendants-Respondents,
and
Lehigh Marine, LLC, Defendant. C-1023 Sept. Term 2018
082438 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000335-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
